# Knowledge Explorer Demo

Output docs/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 900
Set Height 700
Set Padding 15
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Hide
Type "export PATH=$HOME/.local/node-current/bin:$PATH"
Enter
Type "cd ~/Desktop/knowledge-explorer"
Enter
Type "alias knowledge-explorer='node dist/index.js'"
Enter
Type "export PS1='$ '"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "knowledge-explorer --render-only"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 15s
